1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:58,119
The noble ladies' selection begins.

3
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,680
Strip.

4
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,760
Hurry!

5
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,480
All of you here today

6
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,159
are daughters of noble clans.

7
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:22,439
Soon,

8
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:24,200
you'll be serving His Majesty.

9
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:26,519
How dare you lowly servants
humiliate them?

10
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:31,760
Whether you enter the palace

11
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,879
depends on your fortune.

12
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,640
First trial today:

13
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,879
if you refuse,

14
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:37,920
then all of you

15
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,799
get out!

16
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,760
(Now,)

17
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,719
(I have nothing left to lose.)

18
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,680
(I just need to remember,)

19
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,319
(within these walls,)

20
00:01:58,799 --> 00:02:01,640
(by any means and at any cost,)

21
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:03,879
(I will)

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,439
(annihilate them all.)

23
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:11,700
=Episode 1=

24
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,639
(Wedding)
Hear me, Zhao Tribe, land of surrender.

25
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,479
By decree of the Kun Emperor,

26
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:22,000
the Imperial Preceptor is sent
to escort your Holy Maiden to court.

27
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:25,400
To ensure stable diplomacy,

28
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:29,080
(Zhao Tribe's Chieftain and Consort)
surrender the Holy Maiden to us now.

29
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,800
(Feng Ye, Imperial Preceptor of Kun)
Lord Nine-Thousand,

30
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,800
(Lord Nine-Thousand)
my tribe

31
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,719
has paid tribute for three years.

32
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:37,360
And all know

33
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,439
that our land

34
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,759
has sent its only Holy Maiden

35
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,240
to the Kun Kingdom.

36
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,080
Please,

37
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,759
when you return,

38
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,000
report this to His Majesty.

39
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,840
Let him see the truth!

40
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,960
Chieftain,

41
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,159
the Holy Maiden His Majesty wants

42
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:52,560
must be alive.

43
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,840
Open the coffin.

44
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,560
Sang.

45
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,840
How can this be?

46
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:15,599
My Sang!

47
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:19,000
Since I came all this way,

48
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,719
I'm definitely taking someone back.

49
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,319
The Zhao Tribe

50
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:26,080
has only one Holy Maiden!

51
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,319
My Lord.

52
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,159
Chieftain.

53
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:37,719
I'll give you one more chance.

54
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:39,479
Comply,

55
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:42,080
and your tribe will be safe.

56
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,319
Indeed.

57
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:46,840
We do have another daughter.

58
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:49,560
She wields
the Soul-Seizing Divine Power

59
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,840
and has been locked in the dungeon.

60
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,319
Years ago,

61
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,319
I gave birth to Yusang and Yukui.

62
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:58,000
The diviner foretold

63
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,280
that twins

64
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,800
bring one fortune and one disaster.

65
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,159
The elder, Yusang,

66
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:05,240
(Jiang Yusang, Zhao Twin Elder Sister)
is the omen of good,

67
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,879
(Jiang Yusang, Zhao Twin Elder Sister)
gentle of heart.

68
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,800
(Jiang Yukui, Zhao Twin Younger Sister)
The younger, Yukui, is the omen of doom,

69
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,439
(Jiang Yukui, Zhao Twin Younger Sister)
keeping a low profile.

70
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,879
If you take her back, My Lord,

71
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,479
I fear

72
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,920
she will bring the Kun Kingdom

73
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,000
utter ruin!

74
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:21,560
One crowned, one crazed

75
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,079
When camellias bloom, heads will fall

76
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,600
The doomed one laughs

77
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,040
And madness spreads through all

78
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,199
Kui.

79
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,519
When camellias bloom,

80
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:34,360
twin shadows appear.

81
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,839
One flower, one life,

82
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,240
bound together.

83
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:39,279
With this blood mark,

84
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,800
even if we are miles apart,

85
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,920
we will still

86
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,480
feel each other,

87
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,480
until one of us dies.

88
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,279
(Sang)

89
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,560
My Lord,

90
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,519
where is the Holy Maiden?

91
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,240
(My sister)

92
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:33,360
(is dead.)

93
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,639
The rhyme.

94
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,920
Sing it again.

95
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:39,759
When camellias bloom, heads will fall

96
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:40,920
The doomed one laughs

97
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,319
And madness spreads through all

98
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:47,639
She ran.

99
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,079
My Lord,

100
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,160
do we proceed with the plan?

101
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:56,240
Find a decoy to pose as the Holy Maiden.

102
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,399
General Rong Xiu fears my rising merit.

103
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,160
He will surely ambush us on our return.

104
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,319
Be careful on the road.

105
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,040
Yes.

106
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,560
(You've been gone for three years.)

107
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,800
(You became the emperor's consort,)

108
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:22,319
(so why...)

109
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,000
This is...

110
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,199
Come. Join me

111
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,800
for a game.

112
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:47,680
(My sister was humiliated like this.)

113
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,759
My Palace of Punishment.

114
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:55,920
Do you like it?

115
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:02,720
Kui,

116
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,920
though you possess the Divine Power,

117
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,680
remember, this power

118
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,319
must never be abused.

119
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,120
My dear sister.

120
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,439
Rest in peace.

121
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:18,120
Those who harmed you,

122
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,720
none of them will be spared.

123
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:24,519
The Holy Maiden departs!

124
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:26,959
Clear the way!

125
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:29,100
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

126
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:35,399
The Lord was right.

127
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,279
Someone did come to assassinate her.

128
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:45,519
Don't let him take her into the palace.

129
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,759
Kill the Holy Maiden!

130
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:39,480
(So this is the Divine Power?)

131
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,720
(Interesting.)

132
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:52,679
Pleasure.

133
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:55,440
Jiang Yukui.

134
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,759
Can you let me go first?

135
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:11,200
You're sending her to the palace

136
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:14,080
just to plant a needle

137
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,399
by the Emperor's side.

138
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,279
I think

139
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:20,480
I'm better suited to be that needle.

140
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,200
Reason?

141
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,519
Look.

142
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,960
The wedding procession,

143
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,159
so many guards,

144
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:29,480
tight as a fortress.

145
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:33,080
How did I get inside the sedan

146
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,639
without anyone noticing?

147
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,679
I know only you

148
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:38,200
can get me to the Emperor.

149
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,120
I can help you.

150
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,679
(If you take her back, My Lord,)

151
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:48,120
(I fear)

152
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,279
(she will bring the Kun Kingdom)

153
00:09:50,279 --> 00:09:52,440
(utter ruin!)

154
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:55,039
Intriguing.

155
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,519
(If you want to be my needle,)

156
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,840
(first pass the three trials.)

157
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,159
(The first:)

158
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:06,840
(survive the noble ladies' selection.)

159
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:08,840
Strip.

160
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:23,559
(She didn't shrink away
despite being a Holy Maiden.)

161
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:27,519
(Is it because she's been locked
in the dungeon all these years?)

162
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,759
(If that's the case,)

163
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:37,480
she's got some nerve.

164
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,519
Keep stripping.

165
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,919
To enter the palace,

166
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,679
you must have assets.

167
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:57,120
A woman's appearance is one.

168
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,720
Her skin is another.

169
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,879
Only with tender skin

170
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,159
can it remain

171
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:11,559
completely dry.

172
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:25,559
A maiden's qi is pure.

173
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,399
A married woman's qi is turbid.

174
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,000
If she is a virgin,

175
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,480
the air below

176
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,080
is like a gentle breeze.

177
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:43,240
Drag her out.

178
00:11:44,039 --> 00:11:44,559
Matron!

179
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:45,399
I didn't!

180
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,879
Matron!

181
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:49,960
(The first trial was that simple?)

182
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:09,820
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

183
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:11,740
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

184
00:12:11,940 --> 00:12:15,060
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

185
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:19,180
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

186
00:12:22,140 --> 00:12:23,860
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

187
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,380
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

188
00:12:25,740 --> 00:12:29,140
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

189
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:33,140
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

190
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:37,460
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

191
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:41,020
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

192
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:43,340
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

193
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:47,540
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

194
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:49,620
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

195
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:51,140
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

196
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:54,340
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

197
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:56,660
♪In dreams, it's you♪

198
00:12:56,660 --> 00:12:58,060
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

199
00:12:58,060 --> 00:13:01,380
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

200
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:04,780
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

201
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:08,340
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

202
00:13:08,340 --> 00:13:11,580
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

203
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:15,020
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
